Package: node-postcss
Version: 6.0.23-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Debian Javascript Maintainers <pkg-javascript-devel@lists.alioth.debian.org>
Installed-Size: 807
Depends: nodejs, node-chalk (>= 2.3.0), node-supports-color (>= 4.4.0), node-source-map (>= 0.6.1)
Section: javascript
Priority: optional
Homepage: http://postcss.org/
Description: Tool for transforming styles with JS plugins
 These plugins can lint your CSS, support variables and mixins, transpile
 future CSS syntax, inline images, and more.
 .
 PostCSS is used by industry leaders including Wikipedia, Twitter, Alibaba,
 and JetBrains. The [Autoprefixer] PostCSS plugin is one of the most popular
 CSS processors.
 .
 Node.js is an event-based server-side JavaScript engine.
